    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\text{Since } f(1) = 1, f(2) = 4, f(3) = 9, \\text{ we have } \\overrightarrow{MN} = (1; 2; 3). \\text{ Call } Q(x; y; z), \\text{ we have } \\overrightarrow{QP} = (7 - x; 7 - y; 5 - z). \\\\ \\text{Since } \\overrightarrow{MN} = \\overrightarrow{QP}, \\text{ we have } \\begin{cases} 7 - x = 1 \\\\ 7 - y = 2 \\\\ 5 - z = 3 \\end{cases} \\Leftrightarrow \\begin{cases} x = 6 \\\\ y = 5 \\\\ z = 2 \\end{cases} \\Rightarrow Q(6; 5; 2).\n$$"
